name 'emma-test-computational-thinking-python-twowayselection-CFU'
title 'Check for Understanding'

wrong 'Red background'
wrong 'Red line'
wrong 'Green star'
right 'Green line'
allow_multiple_attempts true

markdown <<MARKDOWN
What will the Painter paint if the `user_number` is `10` and the `user_color` is `green`?
```
if user_number > 5 {

   if (user_color == "red") {
      paint background(user_color)
   }
   else {
      paint line(user_color) 
   }

else {
    paint star(user_color)
   }
}
``` 
MARKDOWN
